{"tid":1105212,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的 頭先搭小巴遇著嗰傻佬","createTime":"2019-04-13T17:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T22:36:57.000Z","uid":248215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3b93f6322f981b1bffbba7b19b60f42cc7b6d490","tid":1105212,"uid":248215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"我拎住好大袋嘢 逼於無奈既情況下要坐雙人位<br />\n因為貪可以將袋嘢放係腳下<br />\n咁我就坐入面既 反正自己尾站先落車<br />\n見到有個其貌不揚既男人上車 之後佢坐正我隔離  <br />\n佢坐落黎隨即向我舉手示意 好似話佢有可能撞到我咁 又係咁用怪異目光打量我 <br />\n我儘量同佢零眼神交流應該冇問題<br />\n一個掟彎 佢砰一聲噠左落地 仲要唔肯起身 <br />\n司機好聲叫人扶佢先起身 <br />\n之後成程車係咁挨埋黎 我好懷疑成件事扮出黎<br />\n有乜可能唔捉實扶手 成個人飛落地<br />\n附上一張 我雙手揸實扶手既圖<br />\n我成程車都捉實扶手 用手踭撐住佢 <br />\n費事佢挨哂埋黎 攰過玩奧運五環 <br />\n我係到奉勸各位 自己一個最好都係揀單人位<br />\n香港真係好多傻佬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aK5WEzq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaK5WEzq.png&h=c35e6183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7515d807f37942c8cd74f54bfec5d90590c5b49","tid":1105212,"uid":208235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"👌"},{"pid":"9080cda6220965d6b7676ef93ad2748adf93209a","tid":1105212,"uid":247760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:21:29.000Z","msg":"k可能真係智商有障礙啫"},{"pid":"3d8c3447ea3b1ebbde7ce801ed141cd8babd68a5","tid":1105212,"uid":182178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:24:14.000Z","msg":"我試過有次搭小巴隔離個學生成程攞背脊埃住我<br />\n不過幾靚仔我又冇乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n利申巴"},{"pid":"ccc50b16329b864117b64390d05abd10e1c3b674","tid":1105212,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:34:08.000Z","msg":"係囉啲麻甩佬真係勁乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都借啲倚搏懵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好乞人憎！！！"},{"pid":"079a3eca3f71dfa1c7b28ccb52dbc6270e40e438","tid":1105212,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其貌不揚既男人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主反感原因 講完"},{"pid":"137a3ea3f9c9d7777f44deeebe9a91c5f1e957fe","tid":1105212,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:17:21.000Z","msg":"明顯係抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebef21d30e0450164445c117733db8488581ba0","tid":1105212,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:38:36.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6198a426a1afb746ea06c278a56417d1bcca798f","tid":1105212,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T22:36:57.000Z","msg":"你唔好咁痴線啦"}]}